Get a treatment at Dewskin with me! ✨

First, we discuss what your skin goals are. Then Leah creates a customized treatment for you based on those and your skintype. 

Not sure what love your skin needs? Leave it to the expert with Dewskin’s custom DEW facial. 💦 This incredible facial is customized and tailored to YOUR skin. 

Take a load off, relax and let Leah take care of what your skin needs! We promise - you are in great hands 🤝

and in the blink of an eye, Dewskin turned ONE! 😭🎉

to my clients, followers, friends & family: THANK YOU for supporting and loving this solo aesthetician and her toy poodle! Thank you for trusting me with your skin. Thank you for believing in me when I took a leap of faith and opened Dewskin. Thank you for buying gift cards. Thank you for your referrals. Thank you for being flexible with my schedule at times. Thank you for liking my posts, commenting, sharing. Thank you for writing such amazing reviews. Thank you for allowing me to be myself and share my passion with you all. I love this community so much. You all give me purpose and I am forever grateful!!!!

if you are scared to open your own business- don’t be. Fear is not real. The only place fear can exist is in our thoughts of the future. There will be risks but there will be many more rewards. Is it easy? No, but nothing worth fighting for is easy. Is it worth it? 💯%!!! 

2024 is the year of commitment for me, both personally and professionally and I am HERE FOR IT!!! I get to marry my best friend in May and I have so many exciting plans for this growing business! Believe me when I say, Dewskin is JUST getting started 🙌🏻

Cheers to healthy glowing skin in 2024!

SO MUCH LOVE TO YOU ALL! 

 Xx your Skin BFF 🫶🏼

THE BUILD OUT OF DEWSKIN✨

I thought I would post this transformation a lot sooner than now, but being Dewskin’s one year anniversary, I thought it was the perfect time to finally share!

When I first told Ryan that I wanted to open up Dewskin, he thought it was a crazy idea due to the fact I had only been an aesthetician for two years and I didn’t have a full book of clients yet. I always dreamt of having my own business I just didn’t know if/when that would happen. Well, this “crazy idea” turned into a reality in less than 2 months. Once I found the space and signed the lease, we had 18 days (yes you read that right) to completely transform an outdated law firm into a beautiful modern Medspa! Let’s just say we didn’t sleep those 18 days 😅 It was a VERY short timeframe, I wanted to be open by the beginning of 2023 and my incredible fiancé as well as help from my amazing family made it happen and I couldn’t be more grateful! 

Creating an environment where my clients feel comfortable and look forward to coming in for their treatments is exactly what I envisioned, and I truly hope that I did a good job bringing my vision to life! 

Love you all!

Xx your skin BFF
